## Notion MCP

### Sintaxis correcta (Claude Code)

```
# Buscar paginas/DBs
notion-search: "query"

# Leer pagina o DB
notion-fetch: page_id o database_id

# Query DB con filtros
notion-database-query: database_id + filters

# Crear pagina en DB
notion-create-pages: parent_id + properties

# Actualizar pagina
notion-update-page: page_id + properties
```

### Errores comunes (de OpenClaw — no repetir)
- NO usar `database_id` donde pide `data_source_id` (y viceversa)
- Los IDs incorrectos estan en `.claude/context/notion-registry.md` → seccion "IDs INCORRECTOS"

### CRM: actualizar Outreach Status
```
Usar notion-update-page con:
  property: "Outreach Status"
  value: "Discovery Booked" (o el stage que corresponda)

Stages validos: Not Contacted → 1st-6th TP → En Conversacion → Discovery Booked
→ Closing Booked → Send Proposal → Negotiations/Pending Payment → Closed Won/Lost
```

